<template>
  <HelloWorld msg="Welcome to NEU Library System"/>
  <Otherwebsite/>
</template>

<script>
import HelloWorld from './components/HelloWorld.vue'
import Otherwebsite from './components/otherwebsite.vue'
export default {
  name: 'App',
  components: {
    HelloWorld,
    Otherwebsite
  }
}
import {
    provideFluentDesignSystem,
    fluentAccordion,
    fluentAccordionItem
} from "@fluentui/web-components";

provideFluentDesignSystem()
    .register(
        fluentAccordion(),
        fluentAccordionItem()
    );
</script>

<style>
#app {
  font-family: Avenir, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  text-align: center;
  color: #2c3e50;
  margin-top: 60px;
  
}


</style>
